dct_description_sm: Shows portions of Minnesota, Iowa, Wisconsin, and Illinois.; "8-'29"--lower right in neat line; "September 1929 (25M)--lower margin."; Relief shown by shading.; Shows airways, air distances at 10 mile intervals, and stops in red; railroads and cities shown in black.; On verso: schedule, text, and ill.
42 x 48 centimeters, folded to 23 x 11 centimeters
